# qemu

	qemu -cdrom binary.iso

Qemu might be a little slow if you don't have the qemu kernel module running.

## Testing the hard drive [[installer]] on ISO

Create the hard drive:

	qemu-img create test.qcow2 10G

Setup [tap networking](http://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Qemu#Tap_Networking_with_QEMU):

	sudo qemu -enable-kvm -net nic -net tap,ifname=tap0 -cdrom /tmp/webconverger.2009-09-09.5.5-iso.iso

**BUG** The installed webconverger has a login prompt. in-target must have failed.

